00:17:39.380 --> 00:17:42.460
<i>I don't really know how to have fun at night.</i>

00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:46.250
<i>I go on walks, drink booze, or play video games...</i>

00:17:46.250 --> 00:17:48.210
<i>That's about all I know,</i>

