Nazuna-chan, I want to apologize!

00:18:57.790 --> 00:19:00.460
No need, that's all over already.

00:19:00.460 --> 00:19:02.040
Huh?! It's not over though!

00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:04.460
Seriously! It's done!

00:19:04.460 --> 00:19:08.080
