to make Yamori-kun fall for you.

00:19:21.750 --> 00:19:24.580
That's the condition for us not killing him.

00:19:25.290 --> 00:19:27.580
Sure, it's been fun.

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:31.130
So much so that I forgot that I'd been bored for ages.

00:19:31.330 --> 00:19:34.920
That's not any different from our initial agreement, is it?

00:19:36.130 --> 00:19:39.920
I hung out with you like a know-it-all just to look cool.

00:19:40.460 --> 00:19:43.330
But I never intended for any of it to be a lie.

00:19:43.790 --> 00:19:45.000
Sorry.

00:19:45.580 --> 00:19:49.080
Everything we did was so new and fresh to me.

00:19:50.630 --> 00:19:52.710
I'm sorry about our date.

00:19:53.210 --> 00:19:55.790
But it was fun in the end.

00:19:56.630 --> 00:19:57.830
That's why...

00:19:57.960 --> 00:19:59.330
<i>That's why I have to say it.</i>

00:19:59.540 --> 00:20:01.920
<i>Ko-kun, Ko-kun, I promise...</i>

00:20:03.710 --> 00:20:05.040
Then we're okay!

00:20:05.960 --> 00:20:08.420
Me too! I had fun, too!

00:20:08.790 --> 00:20:10.630
Everything was new to me.

00:20:11.210 --> 00:20:16.460
