keep finding new things to do!

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:19.750
You and me both, we're no good at being alone.

00:20:22.420 --> 00:20:25.670
Nazuna-chan, I'm going to fall in love with you!

00:20:26.500 --> 00:20:30.000
So, I won't let you ever get bored.

00:20:30.000 --> 00:20:31.250
Let's stay together!

00:20:35.920 --> 00:20:37.880
Uh, s-sorry!

00:20:37.880 --> 00:20:41.330
I got too excited and I wasn't thinking
about how to phrase things!

00:20:42.460 --> 00:20:45.500
I'm just glad you're not hurt, Nazuna-chan.

00:20:46.040 --> 00:20:49.290
<i>Ko-kun, Ko-kun, I promise...</i>

00:20:49.460 --> 00:20:52.250
I was really worried they might actually kill you.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:58.920
<i>...I'll become a vampire worth falling for.</i>

